# 🌞 Solar Panel Tracking System (Mechanical + Embedded)

## 📌 Description
A zero-power solar panel tracking system using a gear-driven mechanism to follow the sun’s movement throughout the day. Includes a manual key-based reset for alignment, ensuring efficient energy capture even during cloudy conditions with no external power required.

## ⚙️ Features
- Zero-power gear-driven operation  
- Tracks sun movement reliably  
- Manual key reset for alignment  
- Sustainable and low-maintenance  

## 🔩 Components
- Gear system  
- Shaft & bearings  
- Solar panel mount  
- Manual reset key  
- Supporting frame  

## 📐 Workflow
1. Panel starts facing east.  
2. Gear system rotates panel following sun.  
3. Works even during cloudy conditions.  
4. Manual key resets alignment for next sunrise.  

## 🚀 Benefits
- Improves energy capture efficiency  
- No electrical power required  
- Eco-friendly and cost-effective  

